{"tid":479867,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"做老師嘅 千祈唔好亂咁對一個學生嘅能力下定論","createTime":"2017-11-25T14:29:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-25T15:33:36.000Z","uid":10277,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"396a02e9ace1ac34fecd22a015b24f8b321d7e98","tid":479867,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T14:29:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/25/220419_ad2349012abf4e24c1fd73ddb5d8fbae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F25%2F220419_ad2349012abf4e24c1fd73ddb5d8fbae.jpg&h=3c1cd2cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第54屆金馬獎(2017)，應屆「動畫及視覺特效」課程畢業生石家俊、黃俊朗、黃梓瑩，憑畢業作品《暗房夜空》獲得「最佳動畫短片」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/25/220722_439e8bce51018aef7db3c51cc685c62a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F25%2F220722_439e8bce51018aef7db3c51cc685c62a.jpg&h=eb7485af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《暗房夜空》以紀錄動畫片形式探討性小眾議題，同時描述香港年輕同志 Adam如何爭取權益及與其父親矛盾複雜嘅關係。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話完人質素一般甚至去到差 仲要無一有驚喜<br />\nHD有時候都好過你<br />\n<br />\n但係人地畢業作拿金馬獎.... <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c3ab6d1caa49e5d27abbf20df0c36318eaea29","tid":479867,"uid":61752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T14:55:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f410d2674e1be79bbb2108c80819df23b8ade02","tid":479867,"uid":22609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T15:00:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37bea5b5800231d540931ae0f3cda5348c4c7654","tid":479867,"uid":38177,"like